<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Order date</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Limit the orders for which dunning letters are generated by selecting a start and end date from the calendar. The orders from the chosen period of time are found.</p></td>
